rows.label: tlk47300161_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey...
You heard about Kisra on Emi Island?

rows.label: tlk47300161_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently they've got a bit of a
Dringworm problem there.

rows.label: tlk47300161_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Listen up! Dringworms are those nasty
shelled beasties that feed on Divine Beasts.
Thought everybody knew that...

rows.label: tlk47300161_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Few hundred years back, they filled an
island with holes and it sank into the
Cloud Sea!

rows.label: tlk47300161_04_msg0006
rows.name:
They need clearing out sharpish, but
doubt there's anybody in Liberalitas
who's capable...

rows.label: tlk47300161_04_msg0008
rows.name:
Great! This mission's a tough one, so
don't take any chances,okay?
